USAGE:

    <bgm action="PLAY" bgm="$BGM_NAME" />

        $BGM_NAME       - The name of the background music, see BGM enum for full list.

    <bgm action="STOP" bgm="$BGM_NAME"
     (o) duration="$FADE_DURATION" />

        $BGM_NAME       - The name of the background music, see BGM enum for full list.
        $FADE_DURATION  - How long, in ms, the music will fade out for